    (expand): Reformatted,
    (shift): Likewise,
    (shiftWithNoZeroCrossing): Added API docs.
    * source/org/jfree/chart/axis/junit/NumberAxisTests.java
    (testAutoRange2): Fixed failing test,
    (testAutoRange3): Likewise,
    * NEWS: Added recent updates.

